Chartus API reference
=====================

The API URL is https://chartus.org/api
The interaction protocol is pretty simple. You're sending the HTTP POST request with
action name and action parameters and retrieving a response in JSON format.

For example, the POST request to the Chartus API URL using PHP CURL with CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS equal to something like "action=someAction&foo=1&bar=hello".

You can use, modify or extend provided Chartus API client example, e.g. by adding new API actions into interface.

